msgstr "Django におけるフォーム"

msgid ""
"We've described HTML forms briefly, but an HTML ``<form>`` is just one part "
"of the machinery required."
msgstr ""
"HTML フォームについては簡単に説明しましたが、HTML ``<form>`` は必要となる仕掛"
